âœ… Objective:
To model a UML Use Case Diagram and document use case scenarios for the Inventory Management System, showcasing interactions between users and the system.

ðŸ”§ What is a Use Case Diagram?

A Use Case Diagram is a type of UML (Unified Modeling Language) diagram that shows:

Actors (users/external systems)
Use Cases (system functionalities)
Relationships (how users interact with functionalities)
It helps in understanding the functional scope of the project.

