ðŸ“‘ Use Case Scenarios
ðŸ”¹ Use Case: Upload Sales & Inventory Data

Actor: Shopkeeper
Description: The shopkeeper uploads recent sales and current stock data.
Precondition: Shopkeeper must be logged in.
Postcondition: Data is stored and passed to ML model.
ðŸ”¹ Use Case: Forecast Product Demand

Actor: ML Engine
Description: Predicts future product demand using past sales data.
Trigger: After data upload or scheduled interval.
Postcondition: Prediction results stored for recommendation use.
ðŸ”¹ Use Case: Generate Restocking Suggestions

Actor: Inventory System
Description: Suggests which products need to be reordered and in what quantity.
Trigger: After demand forecast.
Postcondition: Suggestions are visible to shopkeeper.
ðŸ”¹ Use Case: Place Order

Actor: Customer
Description: Customer places an order based on available stock.
Precondition: Items should be in stock.
Postcondition: Inventory is updated.
ðŸ”¹ Use Case: Monitor System

Actor: Admin
Description: Admin checks usage, logs, and model performance.
Postcondition: Admin may initiate re-training or system updates.
